    <string name="about_section_libraries">Libraries</string>
    <string name="about_section_privacy">Privacy</string>
    <string name="about_osm_attribution">© OpenStreetMap contributors. Map data is licensed under the Open Database License (ODbL).</string>
    <string name="about_odbl_notice">OpenStreetMap data is © OpenStreetMap contributors and licensed under the Open Database License (ODbL) 1.0. Any derived database (e.g. the aus-roads map pack) must carry this attribution visibly. See https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright for full terms.</string>
    <string name="about_privacy_posture">This app makes no network requests after the first-time map pack download. No analytics. No ads. No accounts. No background location.</string>
    <string name="about_privacy_full">v0.1 ships offline-only. The AndroidManifest declares no INTERNET and no location permissions. Cloud backup and device-to-device transfer are both disabled. There is no analytics SDK, no crash reporter, no Google Play Services dependency, and no foreground service. The privacy posture is documented in the project repository under docs/notes/privacy.md and reflected in this in-app privacy section.</string>

